sk%20acknowledged%20the%20risk%20to%20the%20world%20if%20the%20development%20of%20AI%20continues%20on%20its%20current%20trajectory%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20direct%20terms%20he's%20used%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20kind%20of%20grow%20an%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAGI.%20It's%20almost%20like%20raising%20a%20kid%2C%20but%20one%20that's%20like%20a%20super%20genius%2C%20like%20a%20God-like%20intelligence%20kid%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20matters%20how%20you%20raise%20the%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20at%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20event%20on%20March%2019%2C%20referring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20I%20think%20that's%20incredibly%20important%20for%20AI%20safety%20is%20to%20have%20a%20maximum%20sort%20of%20truth-seeking%20and%20curious%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20his%20%26quot%3Bultimate%20conclusion%26quot%3B%20regarding%20the%20best%20way%20to%20achieve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feffective-accelerationism-humans-replaced-by-ai-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20to%20grow%20the%20AI%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20forces%20it%20to%20be%20truthful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20force%20it%20to%20lie%2C%20even%20if%20the%20truth%20is%20unpleasant%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20of%20the%20best%20way%20to%20keep%20humans%20safe%20from%20the%20tech.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20important.%20Don't%20make%20the%20AI%20lie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20found%20that%2C%20once%20an%20AI%20learns%20to%20lie%20to%20humans%2C%20the%20deceptive%20behavior%20is%20impossible%20to%20reverse%20using%20current%20AI%20safety%20measures%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Ftech%2Fai-deception-anthropic-artificial-intelligene-b2478699.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20model%20were%20to%20exhibit%20deceptive%20behavior%20due%20to%20deceptive%20instrumental%20alignment%20or%20model%20poisoning%2C%20current%20safety%20training%20techniques%20would%20not%20guarantee%20safety%20and%20could%20even%20create%20a%20false%20impression%20of%20safety%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fpdf%2F2401.05566.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20cited%20by%20the%20outlet%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20troubling%2C%20the%20researchers%20added%20that%20it%20is%20plausible%20that%20AI%20may%20learn%20to%20be%20deceptive%20on%20its%20own%20rather%20than%20being%20specifically%20taught%20to%20lie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20gets%20to%20be%20much%20smarter%20than%20us%2C%20it%20will%20be%20very%20good%20at%20manipulation%20because%20it%20would%20have%20learned%20that%20from%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Hinton%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20'Godfather%20of%20AI%2C'%20who%20serves%20as%20Musk's%20basis%20for%20his%20risk%20assessment%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFAbsoxQtUwM%26ab_channel%3DCNN%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20are%20very%20few%20examples%20of%20a%20more%20intelligent%20thing%20being%20controlled%20by%20a%20less%20intelligent%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Musk%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-20-percent-chance-ai-destroys-humanity-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711929487000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ef0dca90413ab8e