g%20field%20before%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20forcefully%20scuttle%20the%20finances%20of%20Opposition%20parties%20should%20be%20immediately%20stopped%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20said%2C%20without%20mentioning%20the%20freeze%20on%20Congress%20funds%20and%20the%20latest%20Income%20Tax%20notice.%20Action%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20CBI%20and%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20should%20also%20be%20stopped%2C%20she%20said%2C%20reading%20out%20the%20list%20of%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20also%20demanded%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20investigate%20what%20they%20called%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bextortion%26quot%3B%20of%20funds%20through%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BLoktantra%20Bachao%20Rally%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20leaders%20said%2C%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20commitment%20to%20fighting%2C%20winning%2C%20and%20saving%20democracy%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20BJP%20wins%20these%20fixed%20elections%20and%20changes%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20country%20will%20be%20on%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20declared%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20decide%20if%20you%20want%20democracy%20or%20dictatorship...%20Those%20who%20support%20dictatorship%20need%20to%20be%20kicked%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20new%20energy%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20India%20has%20been%20born%20today...%20Today%2C%20the%20slogan%20for%20independence%20is%20being%20raised%20here...%20It%20is%20our%20independence%20that%20our%20Constitution%20and%20our%20republic%20are%20protected.%20We%20will%20gain%20this%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20CPM's%20Sitaram%20Yechury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20declared%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20not%20a%20man%20but%20an%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20arrest%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20but%20how%20will%20you%20arrest%20his%20ideology%3F%20In%20which%20jail%20will%20you%20send%20the%20lakhs%20of%20Kejriwals%20that%20are%20born%20in%20India%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20reiterating%20the%20party%20stance%20on%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20which%20took%20place%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20in%20the%20country.%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20and%20Hemant%20Soren's%20wife%20Kalpana%20Soren%20were%20also%20present%20at%20today's%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20has%20brought%20together%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20which%20was%20making%20more%20headlines%20recently%20over%20its%20differences%20than%20its%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20in%20point%20was%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20decision%20to%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Bengal%2C%20rejecting%20the%20agreed-upon%20sit-sharing%20formula.%20She%20even%20said%20that%20her%20membership%20of%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20on%20hold%20and%20she%20would%20review%20the%20matter%20after%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20party%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20however%2C%20staunchly%20declared%20today%20that%20Trinamool%20%26quot%3Bvery%20much%20was%2C%20is%20and%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20fight%20of%20BJP%20versus%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20also%20comes%20on%20a%20day%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20flagged%20off%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20though%2C%20appeared%20unfazed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20at%20the%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20giving%20the%20slogan%20of%20'400%20paar'.%20If%20you%20are%20going%20to%20win%20more%20than%20400%20seats%2C%20then%20why%20are%20you%20scared%20of%20the%20AAP%20leader%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20sent%20elected%20Chief%20Ministers%20to%20jail.%20Not%20just%20the%20Indians%20but%20the%20whole%20world%20is%20criticising%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20without%20mentioning%20the%20comments%20that%20have%20come%20on%20the%20subject%20from%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20United%20States%20and%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20Opposition%20rally%20was%20meant%20to%20hide%20their%20acts%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20supporting%20those%20who%20have%20looted%20the%20country%20as%20Congress%20has%20also%20looted%20throughout%20their%20tenure.%20From%20the%20days%20of%20Pandit%20Nehru%2C%20the%20Jeep%20scam%20to%20the%20Bofors%20scam%3B%20the%20coal%20scam%20to%20the%20commonwealth%20scam%20and%20the%202G%20scam.%20All%20these%20happened%20while%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Ramlila%20Maidan%2C%20those%20who%20put%20dots%20in%20between%20the%20name%20of%20this%20country%20and%20speak%20about%20saving%20the%20nation%20--%20they%20are%20actually%20there%20to%20save%20their%20family...%20India's%20'tukde%20tukde'%20is%20in%20the%20DNA%20of%20Congress...%20Yuvraj%20is%20not%20even%20ready%20to%20accept%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20and%20he%20also%20demands%20interference%20of%20foreign%20soil%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20BJP's%20Shehzad%20Poonawala.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711911120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fmulha4eg_india-bloc-rally_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-massive-show-of-unity-at-rally-to-support-arvind-kejriwal-5345521%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20bloc's%20rally%20at%20Delhi's%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20this%20afternoon%2C%20was%20a%20massive%20show%20of%20strength%20where%20the%20leaders%20of%20all%20major%20Opposition%20parties%20pressed%20for%20the%20release%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Jharkhand's%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20He%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-massive-show-of-unity-at-rally-to-support-arvind-kejriwal-5345521%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20Data%20A%20Setback%20To%20BJP%3F%20What%20PM%20Modi%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Sunday%20rejected%20the%20suggestion%20that%20the%20electoral%20bond%20issue%20caused%20a%20setback%20to%20his%20government%2C%20saying%20no%20system%20is%20perfect%20and%20any%20shortcoming%20could%20be%20improved%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20those%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bdancing%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20matter%20will%20repent%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTell%20me%20what%20have%20we%20done%20that%20I%20should%20see%20it%20as%20a%20setback%3F%20I%20firmly%20believe%20that%20those%20dancing%20over%20it%20(bond%20details)%20and%20taking%20pride%20in%20it%20are%20going%20to%20repent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Thanthi%20TV%20in%20an%20interview%20when%20asked%20if%20the%20electoral%20bond%20details%20have%20caused%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20it%20is%20due%20to%20the%20electoral%20bond%20system%20put%20in%20by%20his%20government%20that%20the%20sources%20of%20funding%20and%20its%20beneficiaries%20could%20be%20found%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20trail%20is%20available%20today%2C%20it%20is%20because%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20bonds%2C%20he%20said%2C%20asking%20if%20any%20agency%20can%20tell%20about%20the%20sources%20of%20funding%20and%20their%20beneficiaries%20for%20the%20polls%20before%202014%2C%20the%20year%20he%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20system%20is%20perfect.%20There%20can%20be%20shortcomings%20which%20could%20be%20improved%20upon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20cited%20the%20revelations%20following%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%2C%20which%20brought%20all%20information%20related%20to%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20public%20domain%20while%20terming%20the%20anonymous%20funding%20practice%20unconstitutional%2C%20to%20attack%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20firms%20facing%20criminal%20probes%20have%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20big%20buyers%20of%20these%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20PM%20Modi%20asserted%20that%20one%20should%20not%20see%20politics%20in%20everything%20he%20does%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20works%20for%20the%20country%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20is%20its%20big%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20votes%20were%20his%20main%20concern%2C%20then%20he%20would%20not%20have%20done%20so%20much%20for%20the%20northeast%20states%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20his%20government%20ministers%20have%20visited%20the%20region%20for%20over%20150%20times%20and%20he%20himself%20has%20gone%20there%20more%20times%20than%20all%20other%20prime%20ministers%20together%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20because%20I%20am%20a%20politician%20does%20not%20mean%20I%20work%20only%20to%20win%20elections.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20huge%20potential%20which%20must%20not%20be%20wasted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20connects%20different%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20represents%20aspirations%20of%20people%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20votes%20it%20will%20received%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20not%20be%20anti-DMK%20but%20pro-BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20witnessed%20the%20works%20we%20have%20done%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20decided%20that%20this%20time%20it%20wi