t%3B%3A%20Family%20Of%20Child%20Who%20Died%20After%20Eating%20Cake%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20a%2010-year-old%20girl%20who%20died%20after%20eating%20a%20cake%20ordered%20online%20in%20Punjab%20has%20alleged%20the%20health%20department%20did%20not%20help%20them%20at%20all.%20The%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20also%20filed%20five%20days%20after%20she%20died%2C%20her%20family%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20had%20celebrated%20her%20birthday%20on%20March%2024%2C%20and%20died%20hours%20later%20after%20the%20family%20had%20gone%20to%20bed.%20She%20had%20also%20vomited%20the%20cake%20before%20and%20struggled%20to%20breathe%20before%20she%20died%2C%20her%20family%20has%20said.%20Others%20in%20the%20family%20who%20ate%20the%20cake%20had%20also%20fallen%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20local%20media%2C%20and%20it%20came%20to%20national%20attention%20only%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20grandfather%2C%20Harbhanj%20Lal%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20lack%20of%20alertness%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20health%20department%20was%20disturbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20health%20department%20officer%20refused%20to%20take%20the%20sample%20of%20the%20cake%20that%20we%20had%20ordered.%20The%20officer%20insisted%20they%20will%20take%20samples%20only%20from%20the%20shop%20where%20the%20cake%20was%20baked%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20said%20the%20name%20of%20the%20bakery%20in%20the%20bill%20and%20the%20actual%20shop%20were%20different%2C%20indicating%20it%20could%20have%20been%20a%20fly-by-night%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20a%20concept%20that%20is%20gaining%20currency%20due%20to%20its%20flexible%2C%20lightweight%20nature%20of%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20kitchens%20would%20make%20foods%20in%20usually%20one-room%20setups%20to%20take%20online%20delivery%20orders%2C%20and%20package%20the%20foods%20well%20as%20from%20a%20big%20place.%3