22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiny%20Lanka%20Island%20Takes%20Centre%20Stage%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Politics%20Ahead%20Of%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20tiny%20island%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20Palk%20Straight%20has%20become%20the%20hot%20button%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20toehold.%20The%20island%20of%20Katchatheevu%2C%20a%20disputed%20area%2C%20was%20given%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20by%20the%20Congress%20government%20headed%20by%20late%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20through%20an%20agreement%20in%201974.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20now%20posted%20a%20message%20on%20social%20media%20saying%20the%20Congress%20has%20%26quot%3Bcallously%26quot%3B%20given%20it%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEye-opening%20and%20startling!%20New%20facts%20reveal%20how%20Congress%20callously%20gave%20away%20Katchatheevu.%20This%20has%20angered%20every%20Indian%20and%20reaffirmed%20in%20people's%20minds%20-%20we%20can't%20ever%20trust%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeakening%20India's%20unity%2C%20integrity%20and%20interests%20has%20been%20Congress'%20way%20of%20working%20for%2075%20years%20and%20counting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20posting%20a%20report%20by%20Times%20of%20India%20that%20is%20based%20on%20based%20on%20an%20RTI%20reply%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20president%20K%20Annamalai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20raised%20the%20matter%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Meerut%20meant%20to%20flag%20off%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20linked%20it%20to%20the%20capture%20of%20Tamil%20fishermen%20and%20the%20seizure%20of%20their%20boats%20by%20the%20Lankan%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Annamalai's%20RTI%20had%20sought%20details%20on%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20island%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20a%20grouse%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20With%20the%20Congress%20being%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20state's%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20gain%20political%20traction%20in%20the%20state%20dominated%20by%20Dravidian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatchatheevu%20--%20around%2033%20km%20from%20the%20Indian%20coast%20near%20Rameswaram%20--%20has%20been%20a%20disputed%20territory%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20since%20the%20British%20period.%20Back%20then%20both%20nations%20were%20British%20colonies.%20The%20British%2C%20citing%20the%20traditional%20claims%20of%20the%20Ramnad%20zamindari%20of%20Ramanathapuram%2C%20had%20attached%20it%20to%20the%20Madras%20Presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20dispute%20broke%20out%20again%20after%20Independence%20over%20fishing%20rights%20around%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20settle%20the%20discord%20and%20strengthen%20ties%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20the%20government%20headed%20by%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20agreed%20to%20cede%20it%20to%20island%20nation%20under%20the%201974%20%26quot%3BIndo-Sri%20Lankan%20Maritime%20agreement%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20uninhabited%20volcanic%20island%20--%201.6%20km%20in%20length%20and%20around%20300%20m%20wide%20--%20was%20thought%20to%20have%20little%20strategic%20value.%20But%20over%20the%20last%20decades%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20changed%20owing%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20China%20and%20its%20growing%20influence%20over%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Katchatheevu%20Is%20Important%20For%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20fishermen%20who%20go%20into%20the%20area%20and%20face%20action%20from%20the%20Lankan%20authorities%20are%20mostly%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%2C%20which%20ruled%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%201974%2C%20claimed%20the%20Congress%20government%20had%20not%20factored%20in%20its%20views%20before%20signing%20the%20agreement%20with%20Sri%20Lanka.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20party%20had%20held%20multiple%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20headed%20by%20J%20Jayalalithaa%20had%20routinely%20flagged%20the%20issue%20and%20had%20even%20gone%20to%20court%20over%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20ahead%20of%20Lankan%20Prime%20Minister%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe's%20visit%20to%20India%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20had%20written%20to%20PM%20Modi%2C%20asking%20the%20matter%20be%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20to%20PM%20Modi%20later%20as%20well%2C%20after%20multiple%20fishermen%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20Lankan%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20traditional%20fishing%20waters%20that%20Tamil%20fishermen%20have%20relied%20upon%20for%20generations%20are%20getting%20increasingly%20restricted%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20sustain%20their%20livelihood%20impacting%20the%20economic%20stability%20of%20these%20communities.%20This%20also%20threatens%20the%20cultural%20and%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20region%20that%20revolves%20around%20the%20fishing%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20his%20letter%20in%20February%20this%20year.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20number%20of%20arrests%20is%20spiralling%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%202023%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20navy%20arrested%20243%20fishermen%20and%20seized%2037%20boats.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20past%2028%20days%20alone%2C%2088%20fishermen%20and%2012%20boats%20were%20apprehended%20in%20six%20incidents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20Hot%20Button%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20PM%20Modi's%20comments%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20have%20clashed%20over%20Katchatheevu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20DMK%20leader%20RS%20Bharathi%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20%26quot%3Bno%20achievements%26quot%3B%20to%20showcase%20and%20was%20only%20spreading%20%26quot%3Blies%26quot%3B.%20If%20PM%20Modi%20was%20keen%20on%20Katchatheevu%2C%20he%20could%20have%20reclaimed%20that%20island%20during%20his%2010%20years%20in%20office.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20did%20not%20he%20take%20up%20the%20Katchatheevu%20issue%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bharathi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20argument%20has%20been%20seconded%20by%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%20The%20Katchatheevu%20island%20was%20given%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20as%20part%20of%20a%20friendly%20agreement%20in%201974%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20added%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20too%20had%20undertaken%20a%20similar%20%26quot%3Bfriendly%20gesture%26quot%3B%20towards%20Bangladesh%20on%20exchange%20of%20border%20enclaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711904340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fp4g1uuf8_indian-fishermen_625x300_31_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkatchatheevu-row-a-lankan-island-and-elections-in-tamil-nadu-5346932%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tiny%20island%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20Palk%20Straight%20has%20become%20the%20hot%20button%20issue%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20toehold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkatchatheevu-row-a-lankan-island-and-elections-in-tamil-nadu-5346932%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Royal%20Orchid%20Hotels%20to%20add%20up%20to%2035%20properties%20with%202%2C000%20rooms%20in%20FY25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711904287000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F17%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1700243984-1343.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Froyal-orchid-hotels-to-add-up-to-35-propert