%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20time%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20presided%20over%20the%20GOP's%20collapse%20in%20suburban%20communities%20across%20the%20United%20States%2C%20especially%20in%20affluent%20areas%20filled%20with%20college-educated%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202016%20presidential%20election%2C%20Trump%20lost%20traditional%20GOP%20strongholds%20like%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%2C%20and%20Cobb%20County%2C%20Georgia%2C%20a%20preview%20of%20Democratic%20gains%20in%20the%202018%20midterms%20and%20the%202020%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-haley-suburbs-gop-problem-north-carolina-virginia-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20underperformed%20in%20many%20inner-ring%20suburban%20counties%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%20his%20statewide%20vote%20totals.%20This%20pattern%20emerged%20even%20as%20Trump%20was%20already%20heavily%20favored%20to%20secure%20the%20GOP%20presidential%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Trump%20now%20has%20another%20electoral%20math%20issue%20he'll%20have%20to%20tackle%3A%20his%20underperformance%20in%20key%20exurban%20counties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F03%2F30%2Ftrump-gop-primary-voters-exurbs-00149822%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%20examined%201%2C000%20counties%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20voted%20in%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20primaries%20this%20year%2C%20revealing%20the%20extent%20voters%20preferred%20another%20GOP%20standard-bearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20inner-ring%20counties%20across%20the%20county%2C%20many%20exurban%20counties%20still%20tilt%20toward%20the%20Republican%20Party%20and%20often%20elect%20GOP%20lawmakers%20at%20the%20local%20and%20congressional%20levels.%20And%20unlike%20their%20more%20urban%20counterparts%2C%20exurban%20counties%20generally%20boast%20a%20less-concentrated%20number%20of%20vot