0financial%20matters.%20Understanding%20these%20changes%20can%20help%20you%20save%20more%20and%20avoid%20any%20rule-breaking%20headaches.%20It's%20worth%20taking%20some%20time%20to%20learn%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20EPFO%20Rule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwitching%20jobs%20just%20got%20easier%20on%20your%20finances.%20The%20Employees'%20Provident%20Fund%20Organisation%20(EPFO)%20has%20implemented%20an%20automatic%20transfer%20system%20for%20your%20provident%20fund%20balance.%20This%20means%20no%20more%20manually%20requesting%20a%20transfer%20when%20you%20start%20a%20new%20position.%20EPFO%20will%20automatically%20credit%20your%20PF%20balance%20to%20your%20new%20employer's%20account%2C%20ensuring%20a%20seamless%20continuation%20of%20your%20retirement%20savings.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20win%20for%20employee%20portability%20and%20simplifies%20the%20process%20of%20managing%20your%20PF%20across%20different%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Tax%20Regime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20April%201%2C%202024%2C%20the%20new%20tax%20system%20becomes%20the%20default%20option%20in%20India.%20This%20means%20unless%20you%20specifically%20choose%20the%20old%20tax%20system%2C%20your%20taxes%20will%20be%20calculated%20automatically%20under%20the%20new%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20good%20news%3A%20the%20tax%20brackets%20for%20the%20new%20system%20remain%20the%20same%20for%20the%20financial%20year%202024-25%20(tax%20year%202025-26).%20There%20were%20no%20changes%20announced%20in%20the%20recent%20budget.%20Even%20better%2C%20if%20your%20income%20is%20Rs%207%20lakh%20or%20less%20annually%2C%20you%20won't%20pay%20any%20income%20tax%20under%20the%20new%20system!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENPS%3A%20Two-Factor%20Authentication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20April%201%2C%202024%2C%20the%20PFRDA%20will%20implement%20an%20additional%20security%20measure%20for%20the%20National%20Pension%20System.%20This%20enhanced%20system%20involves%20a%20two-factor%20Aadhaar-based%20authentication%20for%20accessing%20the%20CRA%20system%20via%20password.%20The%20announcement%20of%20this%20upgrade%20was%20issued%20through%20a%20circular%20on%20March%2015%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20the%20two-factor%20Aadhaar%20authentication%20system%20aims%20to%20provide%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20security%20to%20authenticate%20fingerprints%20and%20mitigate%20spoofing%20attempts%2C%20thereby%20enhancing%20the%20security%20of%20Aadhaar-authenticated%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20PFRDA%20circular%2C%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20login%20authentication%20will%20be%20integrated%20with%20the%20existing%20User%20ID%20and%20Password-based%20login%20procedure%2C%20facilitating%202-Factor%20Authentication%20for%20accessing%20the%20NPS%20CRA%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PFRDA%20notification%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20bolster%20security%20measures%20for%20accessing%20the%20CRA%20system%20and%20safeguard%20the%20interests%20of%20subscribers%20and%20stakeholders%2C%20additional%20security%20features%20will%20be%20implemented%20through%20Aadhaar-based%20authentication%20for%20login%20to%20the%20CRA%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Aadhaar-based%20login%20authentication%20will%20be%20integrated%20with%20the%20current%20user%20ID%20and%20password-based%20login%20process%20so%20as%20to%20make%20the%20CRA%20system%20accessible%20through%202%20Factor%20Authentication%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Rule%20of%20FasTag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttention%20FASTag%20users!%20%C2%A0Avoid%20toll%20booth%20hassles!%20%C2%A0Get%20your%20FASTag%20KYC%20done%20by%20March%2031st.%20%C2%A0After%20that%2C%20banks%20may%20deactivate%20your%20FASTag%20if%20it's%20not%20updated.%20%C2%A0Without%20KYC%2C%20payments%20won't%20work%2C%20and%20you%20could%20end%20up%20payi