etty%20special.%20I%20think%20when%20we%20were%20watching%20the%20auction%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20(getting%20signed%20by%20CSK)%20happened%2C%20I%20had%20Dave%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Devon%20Conway%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F45400-devon-philip-conway-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDevon%20Conway%3C%2Fa%3E)%20call%20me%2C%20Santner%20messaged%20me%20and%20then%20obviously%2C%20Flem%20(Fleming).%20So%20that's%20pretty%20cool...%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20lads%2C%20not%20just%20the%20overseas%20guys%2C%20but%20the%20Indian%20guys%20are%20such%20good%20people.%20So%20it's%20very%20easy%20to%20get%20along%20with%20people%20in%20a%20team%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Rachin%20said%20on%20joining%20CSK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20how%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Stephen%20Fleming%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F187-stephen-fleming-playerprofile%5C%22%3EStephen%20Fleming%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20always%20available%20for%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20from%20players%20being%20able%20to%20be%20comfortable%2C%20players%20knowing%20their%20roles%20and%20quite%20a%20relaxed%20environment%2C%20which%20makes%20everyone%20feel%20a%20bit%20more%20chill%20and%20can%20get%20along%20a%20bit%20better%2C%20and%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20it's%20a%20hierarchy%20because%20you%20can%20always%20have%20a%20nice%20conversation%20with%20Flem%20if%20you%20want%20to%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20Hussey%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20you%20can%20have%20a%20conversation%20with%20Rutu.%20It's%20all%20pretty%20chill%2C%20which%20for%20me%2C%20helps%20me%20a%20lot%20means%20I%20can%20come%20in%20and%20just%20not%20try%20to%20be%20anyone%20else.%20I%20can%20just%20be%20myself%20in%20that%20environment%20and%20let%20it%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Rachin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChennai%20Super%20Kings%20batting%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Michael%20Hussey%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F617-michael-hussey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMichael%20Hussey%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20'Impact%20Player'%20rule%20has%20lengthened%20their%20batting%20order%2C%20allowing%20former%20skipper%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20to%20come%20in%20as%20late%20as%20number%20eight%20during%20this%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Impact%20Player'%20rule%2C%20introduced%20from%202023%20edition%2C%20allows%20each%20franchise%20to%20name%20five%20substitutes%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20could%20come%20on%20as%20a%20substitute%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20against%20Gujarat%20Titans%20here%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20CSK%20managed%20to%20post%20a%20match-winning%20total%20of%20206%20for%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20seven%20batters%20coming%20out%20to%20bat%2C%20there%20were%20no%20signs%20of%20Dhoni%20coming%20in%20even%20as%20his%20fans%20got%20a%20bit%20impatient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20been%20a%20directive%20from%20head%20coach%20(Stephen)%20Fleming%20to%20keep%20pushing%20the%20game%20forward.%20The%20'Impact%20Player'%20has%20lengthened%20the%20batting%20order%2C%20with%20MSD%20at%20number%20eight%2C%20which%20is%20crazy%2C%20and%20he%20is%20batting%20well%20(in%20the%20nets)%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Hussey%20told%20reporters%20during%20the%20post-game%20media%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20of%20this%2C%20the%20batters%20up%20the%20order%20can%20take%20the%20positive%20(attacking)%20route.%20They%20certainly%20have%20the%20backing%20from%20the%20coaches%20and%20the%20captain.%20Even%20if%20they%20get%20out%20doing%20so%2C%20it's%20fine%2C%20and%20they%20won't%20be%20criticised.%20We%20want%20to%20keep%20playing%20fast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711899960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ffr61eis_w_625x300_31_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fdoesnt-feel-like-its-a-hierarchy-rachin-ravindras-big-csk-revelation-5344059%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20a%20brilliant%20start%20for%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20in%20IPL%202024%20and%20the%20New%20Zealand%20all-rounder%20contributed%20massively%20to%20his%20side's%20victories%20in%20the%20first%20two%20games%20of%20the%20competition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20William%20and%20Kate%20Middleton's%20family%20didn't%20attend%20Easter%20Sunday%20service%20alongside%20King%20Charles%2C%20but%20here%20are%20all%20the%20royals%20who%20did%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225334%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22King%20Charles%20III%20leaving%20Easter%20Sunday%20service%20on%20March%2031%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660966ef16bde8d4ead3ea23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223580%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKing%20Charles%20III%20leaving%20Easter%20Sunday%20service%20at%20t%20St.%20George's%20Chapel.%3Cp%3EWPA%20Pool%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Prince%20and%20Princess%20of%20Wales%20didn't%20attend%20Easter%20Sunday%20service%20with%20the%20royal%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKing%20Charles%20III%20made%20his%20first%20major%20public%20appearance%20since%20announcing%20his%20cancer%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere%20are%20all%20the%20royals%20who%20attended%20the%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Prince%20and%20Princess%20of%20Wales'%20family%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20Easter%20Mattins%20Service%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E