%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-group-s-mehta-family-pledges-rs-5-000-crore-for-social-causes-124033100398_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-group-s-mehta-family-pledges-rs-5-000-crore-for-social-causes-124033100398_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftorrent-group-s-mehta-family-pledges-rs-5-000-crore-for-social-causes-124033100398_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShouldn't%20Take%20It%20Personally%26quot%3B%3A%20Envoy%20Eric%20Garcetti%20Amid%20US%20'Concerns'%20Over%20CAA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20religious%20freedom%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20any%20democracy%2C%20the%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Eric%20Garcetti%2C%20said%20that%20sometimes%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Washington%20can%20%26quot%3Bagree%20to%20disagree%26quot%3B%20on%20certain%20things%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20read%20negatively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20had%20earlier%20said%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bconcerned%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20in%20India%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bclosely%20monitoring%26quot%3B%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Garcetti%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20we%20monitor%2C%20and%20I%20said%20that.%20And%20I%20said%20in%20broad%20strokes%20that%20religious%20freedom%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20any%20democracy.%20Protecting%20minorities%20is%20very%20important.%20That%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20read%20negatively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20it's%20the%20job%20of%20monitoring%20what%20happens.%20That's%20the%20job%20of%20an%20ambassador.%20That's%20the%20job%20of%20a%20state%20department.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs'%20job%20and%20the%20Indian%20ambassador's%20job%20is%20to%20monitor%20and%20to%20report.%20And%20we%20simply%20said%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20US%20too%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bton%20of%20flaws%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20open%20to%20criticism%2C%20while%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20finding%20common%20international%20law%20and%20respecting%20every%20country's%20specific%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20deep%20friendship.%20It's%20very%20respectful.%20Sometimes%20we%20can%20agree%20to%20disagree%20on%20things%20and%20continue%20with%20our%20business%2C%20and%20we%20shouldn't%20take%20it%20with%20thin%20skin.%20We%20shouldn't%20take%20it%20personally.%20Certainly%2C%20I%20open%20up%20the%20United%20States%2C%20I%20say%20all%20the%20time%2C%20from%20a%20place%20of%20humility.%20We%20have%20a%20tonne%20of%20flaws.%20We're%20open%20to%20criticism.%20We%20want%20to%20listen%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Garcetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20for%20all%20of%20us%20is%20to%20find%20common%20international%20law%20that%20we%20can%20all%20be%20a%20part%20of%2C%20try%20to%20implement%20equally%2C%20and%20respect%20the%20specific%20histories%20that%20every%20country%20has.%20And%20the%20more%20that%20you%20know%20about%20that%2C%20the%20better%20positioned%20you%20are%20when%20you%20are%20monitoring%20things%20to%20be%20able%20to%20comment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20after%20the%20US'%20remarks%20on%20CAA%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20strongly%20objected%20to%20it%20and%20termed%20the%20comments%20%26quot%3Bmisplaced%2C%20misinformed%2C%20and%20unwarranted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20during%20a%20weekly%20press%20briefing%2C%20said%20that%20those%20having%20a%20%26quot%3Blimited%20understanding%20of%20India's%20pluralistic%20traditions%26quot%3B%20should%20not%20comment%20on%20India's%20'internal%20matters'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20notified%20rules%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20on%20March%2011%2C%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20rules%2C%20introduced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20and%20passed%20by%20Parliament%20in%202019%2C%20aim%20to%20confer%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants--including%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Parsis%2C%20and%20Christians--who%20migrated%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%20and%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECitizenship%20(Amendment)%20Rules%2C%202024%20enable%20persons%20eligible%20under%20CAA-2019%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20Indian%20citizenship%20and%20applications%20are%20to%20be%20submitted%20in%20a%20completely%20online%20mode%20for%20which%20a%20web%20portal%20has%20been%20provided%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711897020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Feojf0qng_eric-garcetti-_625x300_31_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshouldnt-take-it-personally-envoy-eric-garcetti-amid-us-concerns-over-caa-5345814%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stating%20that%20religious%20freedom%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20any%20democracy%2C%20the%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20Eric%20Garcetti%2C%20said%20that%20sometimes%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Washington%20can%20%26quot%3Bagree%20to%20disagree%26quot%3B%20