s%20why%20they%20are%20behind%20bars%20today%20and%20not%20getting%20bail%20even%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20election%20is%20a%20fight%20between%20two%20camps.%20On%20one%20side%20you%20have%20the%20NDA%20committed%20to%20eradicating%20corruption%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20is%20the%20INDI(A)%20Alliance%20focused%20on%20protecting%20corrupt%20leaders.%20You%20have%20to%20decide%20whether%20corruption%20should%20be%20removed%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20the%20rally%20in%20Meerut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCorrupt%20people%20should%20listen...%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20attacks%20you%20make%20on%20Modi%2C%20this%20is%20Modi%2C%20he%20is%20not%20going%20to%20stop.%20No%20matter%20how%20big%20the%20corrupt%20person%20is%2C%20action%20will%20definitely%20be%20taken.%20The%20one%20who%20has%20looted%20the%20country%20will%20have%20to%20give%20it%20back.%20This%20is%20Modi's%20guarantee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaising%20the%20Katchatheevu%20island%20issue%2C%20PM%20Modi%20accused%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20of%20trying%20to%20harm%20the%20country's%20unity%20and%20sovereignty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20yet%20another%20anti-India%20conduct%20of%20Congress%20has%20been%20exposed.%20The%20island%20of%20Katchatheevu%2C%20which%20lies%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20is%20extremely%20important%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20national%20security%2C%20was%20given%20away%20by%20Congress%20after%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20still%20paying%20for%20the%20misdoings%20of%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20is%20not%20just%20for%20making%20a%20government%20but%20to%20make%20a%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20his%20government%20was%20preparing%20the%20roadmap%20for%20the%20next%20five%20y