%20quarter%20and%20year%20ending%20March%2031%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Infosys%20said%20in%20a%20BSE%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfosys%2C%20which%20competes%20with%20TCS%20and%20Wipro%20and%20others%20in%20the%20market%20for%20IT%20services%20contracts%2C%20is%20scheduled%20to%20declare%20its%20financial%20results%20for%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%20as%20well%20as%20the%20full%20FY24%20on%20April%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengaluru-headquartered%20IT%20company%20also%20said%20it%20has%20received%20an%20order%20for%20assessment%20year%2022-23%20with%20a%20tax%20demand%20of%20Rs%202%2C763%20crore%2C%20including%20interest%2C%20and%20for%20assessment%20year%2011-12%20with%20a%20tax%20demand%20of%20Rs%204%20crore%2C%20interest%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfosys%20has%20received%20assessment%20orders%20for%20subsidiaries%20as%20well%2C%20totalling%20Rs%20277%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20assessment%20orders%20for%20assessment%20years%2021-22%20and%2018-19%2C%20respectively%2C%20with%20total%20tax%20demand%20of%20Rs%20145%20crore%3B%20order%20for%20assessment%20year%2022-23%20with%20a%20tax%20demand%20of%20Rs%20127%20crore%3B%20and%20for%20assessment%20year%2022-23%20entailing%20tax%20demand%20of%20Rs%205%20crore%20--%20all%20of%20them%20inclusive%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20company%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20evaluating%20the%20implications%20of%20these%20orders%20on%20the%20financial%20statements%20for%20the%20quarter%20and%20year%20ending%20March%2031%2C%202024%20and%20also%20evaluating%20filing%20appeals%20against%20these%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20Infosys%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20company%20has%20received%20refund%20orders%20under%20Section%20254%20for%20assessment%20years%2007-08%20and%2008-09%20and%20under%20Section%20154%20for%20assessment%20year%2016-17%2C%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20refund%20amount%20as%20per%20these%