%20Mr%20Bolton%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20don't%20believe%20%5BJoe%20Biden%5D.%20Neither%20do%20I%2C%20because%20it's%20not%20true!%20Firstly%2C%20regarding%20the%20possibility%20of%20overthrowing%20the%20(American)%20republic%2C%20let's%20be%20clear%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20not%20Julius%20Caesar!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20questioned%20if%20he%20thinks%20Mr%20Trump%20had%20Julius%20Caesar-like%20dictatorial%20tendencies%2C%20John%20Bolton%20exclaimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20hasn't%20got%20the%20brains!%20He's%20a%20property%20developer%2C%20for%20God's%20sake!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20Mr%20Bolton's%20remark%20comes%20a%20few%20months%20after%20Mr%20Trump%20said%20that%20he%20would%20act%20like%20a%20dictator%20only%20on%20%E2%80%9Cday%20one%E2%80%9D%20if%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20December%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F06%2Fdonald-trump-sean-hannity-dictator-day-one-response-iowa-town-hall%5C%22%3EAmerican%20writer%20Sean%20Hannity%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20an%20interview%20in%20Iowa%20asked%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20no%20circumstances%2C%20you%20are%20promising%20America%20tonight%2C%20you%20would%20never%20abuse%20power%20as%20retribution%20against%20anybody%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExcept%20for%20day%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Trump%20replied.%20The%20former%20president%20repeated%20his%20assertion.%20%E2%80%9CI%20love%20this%20guy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20about%20Sean%20Hannity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98You're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20dictator%2C%20are%20you%3F'%20I%20said%3A%20%E2%80%98No%2C%20no%2C%20no%2C%20other%20than%20day%20one.%20We're%20closing%20the%20border%20and%20we're%20drilling%2C%20drilling%2C%20drilling.%20After%20that%2C%20I'm%20not%20a%20dictator.'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20hre