.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShatrunjay%20Pratap%20Singh%20is%20a%20filmmaker%20and%20conservation%20in%20Bera%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Singh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20lay%20in%20an%20article%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EVice.%3C%2Fem%3E%20As%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20the%20community%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85574%2Fbera-rajasthan-leopards-mount-abu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereveres%20the%20leopards%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hartnaram%2C%20who%20is%20a%20Rabari%20herdsman%E2%80%99s%20son%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20burst%20firecrackers%20during%20Diwali%20and%20refrain%20from%20playing%20loud%20music%20even%20during%20wedding%20processions%20so%20that%20it%20does%20not%20disturb%20the%20wild%20cats.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mutual%20respect%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20the%20recipe%20for%20the%20harmony.%20And%20seconding%20this%20thought%20is%20a%20conservationist%20Shatrunjay%20Pratap%20Singh%20from%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20call%20of%20the%20wilderness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20certain%20that%20a%20leopard%20will%20not%20harm%20you%20if%20you%20are%20with%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rabari%20community.%20This%20is%20their%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20threatened%20to%20have%20their%20population%20depleted%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246169%2Fladakh-snow-leopard-conservancy-india-trust-saviours-rinchen-wangchuk-tsewang-namgail-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20leopards%20now%20enjoy%20the%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20have.%20And%20as%20any%20local%20will%20tell%20you%20it%20is%20Singh%20behind%20this%20achievement.%20Now%20heading%20the%20Bera%20S