0hills%20surrounding%20the%20area.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20when%20Lord%20Hanuman%20lifted%20the%20Dronagiri%20Parvat%20to%20take%20it%20to%20Lord%20Lakshman%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20it%20broke%20off%20and%20fell%20here.%20Hence%2C%20these%20hills%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20medicinal%20plants%20growing%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20area%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20home%20that%20blends%20into%20nature%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20they%20started%20to%20work%20on%20their%20dream%20home%20and%20opened%20their%20doors%20to%20the%20guests%20in%202022.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20decided%20to%20share%20our%20space%20with%20guests%2C%20we%20have%20hosted%20more%20than%20200%20guests%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20with%20some%20mud%20and%20lots%20of%20love!%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20architectures%2C%20combining%20a%20blend%20of%20Tamil%2C%20Venad%2C%20and%20Chettinad%20styles%20that%20showcase%20the%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20personally%20a%20collector%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F309562%2Fancient-family-collectibles-in-pictures-antique-artefacts-projectors-cameras-stamps-coins%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20collecting%20artefacts%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20area.%20I%20had%20been%20collecting%20a%20lot%20of%20art%20pieces%20and%20decided%20to%20display%20them%20in%20the%20home.%20Some%20of%20these%20pieces%20are%20more%20than%20100%20years%20old%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20Rajchandar%20was%20clear%20about%20from%20the%20beginning%20is%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20use%20natural%20materials%20to%20build%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-